<p> this具有扩展作用域的功能，其功能相当于</p>&#13;
<div class="cnblogs_code">&#13;
<pre><span style="color: #0000ff;">function</span><span style="color: #000000;"> myfunction() {&#13;
        </span><span style="color: #0000ff;">with</span><span style="color: #000000;"> (document) {&#13;
